text: Loran de Munck (born 9 May 1999) is a Dutch artistic gymnast from Haarlem. He competed at the 2021 European Artistic Gymnastics Championships. A year later De Munck won the silver medal at the 2022 European Men's Artistic Gymnastics Championships in the pommel horse event. It was named as a "historic medal" because never before had a Dutchman won a medal in this event. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch gymnasts Category:Sportspeople from Haarlem
